---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About" description="Summit Ledger Books specializes in bookkeeping for real estate investors, property managers, and developers. Learn about our mission and values.">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <img src="/images/website-hero.png" alt="Summit Ledger Books" class="about-hero-img" />
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="section-heading">About Summit Ledger Books</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>Summit Ledger Books was founded with a simple belief: real estate investors and property managers deserve accurate, affordable bookkeeping that actually understands their business. Too many owners spend their evenings wrestling with spreadsheets instead of evaluating their next deal or managing their properties.</p>

      <p>We started Summit Ledger Books to change that. Our bookkeepers specialize in real estate accounting and partner with investors, property managers, and developers to keep financial records organized, accurate, and ready for tax season, lenders, or any audit.</p>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy:</strong> Your books need to be right. We double-check every entry and reconciliation.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> No hidden fees, no surprises. You'll always know exactly what you're paying for.</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> We meet every deadline, every month. Your books are never behind.</li>
        <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> We explain your finances in plain language, not accounting jargon.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who We Serve</h2>

      <p>We specialize in bookkeeping for real estate investors, property managers, real estate developers, and agents. Whether you own a single rental property, manage a portfolio of units, or are developing your next project, we understand the financial complexity of real estate and know how to keep your books clean, organized, and audit-ready.</p>

      <p>Ready to take bookkeeping off your plate? <a href="https://calendly.com/summit-ledger-books/consultation">Book a free consultation.</a></p>
    </div>

    <div class="certifications">
      <h2 class="certifications-heading">Certifications</h2>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <img src="/images/badge-qbo-level-2.png" alt="QuickBooks Online Certification" class="badge-img" />
        <img src="/images/badge-qbo-payroll.png" alt="QuickBooks Payroll Certification" class="badge-img" />
        <img src="/images/book-cert.png" alt="Bookkeeping Certification" class="badge-img" />
        <img src="/images/client-cert.png" alt="QuickBooks Client Certification" class="badge-img" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
